{"tid":1828050,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳若希爆老公鍾意大波女星，點名大馬林明禎","createTime":"2020-01-17T12:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T15:24:23.000Z","uid":215823,"like":4,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ae12816c21d7fbae1e45f65ad2b3003e77d89acf","tid":1828050,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:43:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nk5PooH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnk5PooH.png&h=2b255772&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吳若希穿起bra top，但見身材略為遜色，問到會否希望上圍加大？她笑說：「我着住呢件衫，喺髮型屋整頭髮都有刻懷疑，因為着唔到個壯觀嘅效果，不過我髮型師就話我着得好fashion，要靚同fashion唔可以太有身材，我鍾意fashion啲，我係標準模特兒身材。」至於問到她老公滿意自己的身材嗎？她說：「咁你要問吓佢，佢一時一樣，我見佢IG有follow啲女明星都好有身材，有follow韓國一個女明星，好瘦但好波濤洶湧，又有follow大馬林明禎。我有問過佢鍾意大胸定好忙嘅人，即係冇空(胸)&hellip;&hellip;閒時間嘅人，佢喺我面前當然話鍾意我。」老公喜歡大胸女星，她笑言不會呷醋：「某個程度上我都睇同羡慕身材好嘅女仔，各有各好，大家打和。」"},{"pid":"6c4f0bded5f153b9c86d0ef09c9687743f5cedf4","tid":1828050,"uid":55279,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:45:36.000Z","msg":"許志安: ..."},{"pid":"bc3482d72692dabc56aa5aef3c217af59c9c0d2c","tid":1828050,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:46:22.000Z","msg":"崇禎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef4af28e783e5867de89dfe54f206e003daf218","tid":1828050,"uid":268094,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:46:42.000Z","msg":"佢老公都係衰唔戴套姐<br />\n你估有愛咩<br />\n都未食夠玩夠"},{"pid":"ae2b4b6be8519390b355d113cf3ccadcb74c6911","tid":1828050,"uid":30892,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:56:23.000Z","msg":"佢講嘢真係好撚唔得體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb9875705d8b982076c494c180efb68f54d98d8","tid":1828050,"uid":160916,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ef4af28e783e5867de89dfe54f206e003daf218","tid":1828050,"uid":268094,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17